org.agilewiki.jactor2.core.reactors

Class IsolationReactor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.agilewiki.jactor2.core.reactors.ReactorBase
      • org.agilewiki.jactor2.core.reactors.IsolationReactor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.AutoCloseable, Blade, IsolationBlade, Closeable, Reactor

    public class IsolationReactor
extends ReactorBase
implements IsolationBlade
    Processes each request until completion, processing responses and 1-way messages (e.g. signals) in the order received. The next request is only processed when a result is returned for the current request.

    Requests/responses destined to a different reactor are held until processing is complete for each incoming request/response.
